// Stove Type Statistics Endpoints

### Get All Stove Type Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics

### Get Market Summary
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/market-summary

### Get Top Stove Types by Sales
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/leaderboard/sales

### Get Top Stove Types by Sales (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/leaderboard/sales?limit=5

### Get Most Viewed Stove Types
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/most-viewed

### Get Most Viewed Stove Types (limit 5)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/most-viewed?limit=5

### Get Stove Types by Trend (Increasing)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/trend/increasing

### Get Stove Types by Trend (Stable)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/trend/stable

### Get Stove Types by Trend (Decreasing)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/trend/decreasing

### Get Stove Types by Trend (Invalid)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-type-statistics/trend/invalid

### Get Stove Type Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/statistics

### Get Stove Type Statistics (not found)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999/statistics

### Get Stove Type Statistics (invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/invalid/statistics

### Create Stove Type Statistics
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/10/statistics
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "expectedDropRate": 0.05,
    "rarityRank": 3
}

### Create Stove Type Statistics (missing fields)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/10/statistics
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "expectedDropRate": 0.05
}

### Increment View Count
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/1/statistics/increment-views

### Increment View Count (not found)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999/statistics/increment-views

### Delete Stove Type Statistics
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/10/statistics

### Delete Stove Type Statistics (not found)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/stove-types/99999/statistics
